OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAfter a chilly start, it
OL,6,Fwill be a dry day with variable
OL,7,Famounts of cloud and bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells for many. Feeling cooler
OL,9,Fcompared to previous days. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,12,Fwith an increasing likelihood of wet
OL,13,Fand windy conditions on Friday and
OL,14,Finto the weekend. Risk of gales on
OL,15,FSaturday. Cooler and brighter with
OL,16,Fblustery showers Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
